10:04.680 --> 10:04.860
Right.

10:05.180 --> 10:11.600
But it does not have a stable identity under the transformation of millions of years of evolutionary pressure.

10:11.960 --> 10:13.920
Or what about legal stuff, like a contract?

10:14.140 --> 10:14.820
Perfect example.

10:15.160 --> 10:20.520
A legal contract survives the transformation of being translated into another language, assuming you have a good translator.

10:20.720 --> 10:20.940
Right.

10:21.040 --> 10:21.940
