The initial state X has been subjected to a highly destructive transformation, T, the washing machine.

13:35.220 --> 13:35.300
Yeah.

13:35.360 --> 13:37.800
The physical properties are irrevocably altered.

13:38.260 --> 13:48.480
But if you take that receipt, smooth it out on a table under a bright light, and use your eyes to trace the faint bleeding ink, you can still read the final total.

13:48.580 --> 13:50.020
You can still extract the meaning.

13:50.400 --> 13:50.600
Yeah.

13:50.600 --> 13:52.160
You can see that you spent $45.

13:52.960 --> 14:01.360
The physical paper didn't survive in its original state, but the distinction, the mathematical difference between $45 and $46 did.

14:01.600 --> 14:08.740
Because your visual cortex and your understanding of numerical shapes acted as the reconstruction operator, R.

14:08.840 --> 14:09.600
That was the operator.

14:09.600 --> 14:10.200
You were.

14:10.620 --> 14:15.580
You performed computational work to recover the distinction from a highly degraded trace.

14:16.540 --> 14:24.680
Flyxion uses this exact math to prove that invariance is just a lazy, hyper-restrictive, special case of recoverability.

14:24.900 --> 14:25.160
Wait.

14:25.300 --> 14:26.740
Invariance is a special case.

14:26.840 --> 14:27.080
Yes.

14:27.320 --> 14:32.620
Invariance is simply recoverability, where the reconstruction operator is the identity operator,

14:32.620 --> 14:39.440
meaning you have to exert zero computational effort to recover the distinction, because the transformation didn't change it at all.

14:39.720 --> 14:40.060
Oh, I see.

14:40.140 --> 14:41.340
It's like a persistence freebie.

14:41.440 --> 14:41.760
Exactly.

14:41.940 --> 14:44.020
But in the real world, you almost always have to pay a toll.

14:44.100 --> 14:45.920
You have to do the actual work of reconstruction.

14:46.580 --> 14:48.880
And that brings us right back to the cave painters in Portugal.

14:48.880 --> 14:52.940
It's the exact same mathematics, just scaled over tens of thousands of years.

14:53.400 --> 14:53.500
Right.

