16:07.960 --> 16:08.500
Exactly.

16:08.640 --> 16:12.180
But, you know, this immediately forces a massive question.

16:12.320 --> 16:12.480
Yeah.

16:12.480 --> 16:15.900
The universe inherently leans toward entropy.

16:16.760 --> 16:17.800
