35:10.460 --> 35:10.820
Exactly.

35:11.260 --> 35:15.020
Wisdom prevents us from optimizing for a local peak that eventually drops off a cliff.

35:15.400 --> 35:18.520
Wisdom preserves optionality, robustness, and systemic health.

35:18.520 --> 35:22.720
And finally, at the very top of this epistemic ladder, we reach the apex.

35:23.340 --> 35:23.780
Truth.

35:24.200 --> 35:24.800
The summit.

35:25.000 --> 35:26.600
And truth isn't just a fact.

35:27.000 --> 35:27.700
It's an alignment.

35:27.980 --> 35:30.120
Truth is not a primitive element you start with.

35:30.680 --> 35:35.660
Truth is the culmination of stable alignment across all these reconstructive structures.

35:35.740 --> 35:37.220
It's the whole stack working together.

35:37.300 --> 35:44.540
It is a structural correspondence between our internal models and the external world that survives transformations across the broadest possible domains.

35:44.540 --> 35:50.360
