The baseball flying through the air is a persistence trajectory.

42:05.060 --> 42:09.620
It carries specific constraints, its mass, its velocity, its structural integrity.

42:09.620 --> 42:14.980
The window also has constraints, mainly the tensile strength of the glass.

42:15.760 --> 42:21.600
When they intersect, the baseball doesn't force the window to break in a classical Newtonian pushing sense.

