What does it do then?

42:22.700 --> 42:28.040
The constraints of the baseball's trajectory alter the mathematical admissibility domain of the window's distinctions.

42:28.360 --> 42:33.220
It changes the rules of what is allowed to exist in that specific region of space-time.

42:33.420 --> 42:33.980
Precisely.

42:33.980 --> 42:39.140
The window shatters because its previous structural distinctions, being a solid, flat sheet of glass,

42:39.340 --> 42:45.120
are literally no longer admissible under the new, overwhelming constraints introduced by the arrival of the baseball.

42:45.300 --> 42:45.600
Wow.

42:45.800 --> 42:49.320
The shattered glass is the only continuation that the universe will permit.

42:50.160 --> 42:54.040
Causality is just the propagation of constraint through the persistence manifold.

42:54.560 --> 42:59.160
It is all one unified, geometric structure of recoverable distinction.

42:59.520 --> 43:03.220
We've gone from ancient DNA to the geometry of cause and effect.

43:03.220 --> 43:06.860
And I think my understanding of reality has been fundamentally rewired.

